{
  "text": "The feeder data for this example were obtained from [CITATION_1] . The feeder was modified to include the Th\u00e9venin equivalent representation of the grid, in accordance with Fig. 3 . Shunt capacitors were placed at nodes 7 and 10 to ensure predisturbance voltages were within allowable bounds of 2%. All non-PEV demand was modelled as voltage dependent (constant current characteristic) unless otherwise noted.",
